# Ruby on Rails

- [README.md](mdc:README.md)

- We have rails tests setup. To run the ruby on rails test suite, run `bin/rails test`. Always run tests after modifying code to ensure our existing application still works

- We can run `bin/brakeman` to test our app security. After major changes (like the implementation of a completely new controller), we should run `bin/brakeman` to look for security issues

- We can run `bin/rubocop` to check for linting errors. Try to follow this `.rubocop.yml`:
```yml
# Omakase Ruby styling for Rails
inherit_gem: { rubocop-rails-omakase: rubocop.yml }
```

- When working with GraphQL all our ruby fields on GraqhQL types from app/graphql/types will be written in snake_case in our ruby code, but will appear as camelCase when interacting with the GraphQL API
